                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\"><placeName>New Orleans</placeName>\n                <date>May 17th 1848</date>.</p>\n            <p>\n                <addressee>Mr Isaac Leeser</addressee>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">Dear Sir</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(4)\">As I promised you<lb/> some days ago in a letter covering check by\n                    <persName>B B Hart</persName><lb/> on <persName>A L Hart</persName> for 50# I\n                now proceed to furnish you<lb/> the names of such as have paid for their\n                subscription<lb/> as handed to me by my Brother</p>\n            <table cols=\"3\" rows=\"15\">\n                <row>\n                    <cell>\n                        <date>48 &amp; 9</date>\n                    </cell>\n                    <cell>\n                        <persName>J L. &amp; E. S. Levy</persName>\n                    </cell>\n                    <cell>6.00</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>“</cell>\n                    <cell>\n                        <persName>A Emanuel</persName>\n                    </cell>\n                    <cell>6.00</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>“</cell>\n                    <cell>\n                        <persName>Edw. Lem</persName>\n                    </cell>\n                    <cell>6.00</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>“</cell>\n                    <cell>\n                        <persName>B Ries</persName>\n                    </cell>\n                    <cell>6.00</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>\n                        <date>1847 &amp; 8</date>\n                    </cell>\n                    <cell>\n                        <persName>J Rodriguez</persName>\n                    </cell>\n                    <cell>6.00</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>\n                        <date>1848 &amp; 49</date>\n                    </cell>\n                    <cell>\n                        <persName>B. Florance</persName>\n                    </cell>\n                    <cell>6.00</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell><date>48</date>.</cell>\n                    <cell>\n                        <persName>H. Florance</persName>\n                    </cell>\n                    <cell>3”</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>“</cell>\n                    <cell>\n                        <persName>A. J. Brome</persName>\n                    </cell>\n                    <cell>3”</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>\n                        <date>'49</date>\n                    </cell>\n                    <cell>\n                        <persName>J. Touro</persName>\n                    </cell>\n                    <cell>3”</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>“</cell>\n                    <cell>\n                        <persName>E. Block</persName>\n                    </cell>\n                    <cell>3.00</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>“</cell>\n                    <cell>\n                        <persName>G. Jonas</persName>\n                    </cell>\n                    <cell>3”</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>“</cell>\n                    <cell>\n                        <persName>S. Magner</persName>\n                    </cell>\n                    <cell>\n                        <hi rend=\"underline\">3”</hi>\n                    </cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell/>\n                    <cell/>\n                    <cell>54.00</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell/>\n                    <cell> less 10 % for collector.</cell>\n                    <cell>\n                        <hi rend=\"underline\"> 5.40</hi>\n                    </cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell/>\n                    <cell/>\n                    <cell>\n                        <hi rend=\"underline\">$48.60</hi>\n                    </cell>\n                </row>\n            </table>\n            <p>I think there was paid into my hands by<lb/>\n                <persName>Mr Block</persName> for one year Back 3#, but I do<lb/> not know exactly,\n                compare his a/c &amp; see if<lb/> it is all paid. <persName>H. Florance</persName>\n                wishes his subscription<lb/> stopped, <persName>J L Levy</persName>, <persName>B. W.\n                    Cohen</persName>, <persName>J Newton</persName>, <persName>L. A.\n                    Gunst</persName><lb/> deny being subscribers &amp; will not pay.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">My Brother <persName>Henry</persName> will endeavor to swell<lb/>\n                the list of your subscribers out here &amp; to do so<lb/> will be glad to have any\n                advice viz whether it<lb/> might not be better to publish in some one or two<lb/>\n                newspapers the fact of an agency being in <placeName>New Orleans</placeName><lb/>\n                &amp; who he is &amp;c &amp;c—as you think best he will do</p>"
                  },
