                {
                  "id": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3f18t18n/manifest/annotation/p2",
                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>I contemplate spending the summer at <persName>Judge Mimce's</persName><lb/> in\n                    <placeName>Frankfort</placeName> in the prosecution of my law studies\n                (altho<lb/> I have been admitted to the practice) and would be glad<lb/> to hear\n                from you there on any subject—He is By the<lb/> way a subscriber—I intended to pay\n                for it for him<lb/> the first year, but he being very curious about our<lb/> people\n                &amp; anxious to learn their habits &amp; study, their<lb/> laws he will no doubt\n                continue a subscriber.<lb/>\n                <persName>Mr Kursheedt</persName> told me (I think) that as ag't he had always<lb/>\n                received a copy of the Occident gratis &amp; that being the case<lb/> I considered\n                the copy which Father had been in<lb/> the habit of receiving would serve for us\n                both and<lb/> you will see I have not collected any subscription<lb/> from him. If\n                this is not satisfactory I will of course<lb/> pay the subscription. I have sold to\n                my Father<lb/> one of the sets of Prayer Books—and will endeavor<lb/> to sell them\n                all as soon as the synagogue creates<lb/> some sensation among the folks—</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">With my Best respects,</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">I remain</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">Very Truly Yours</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(4 )\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">David Labatt</persName>\n            </p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3f18t18n/canvas/p2"
                }
              ]
            }
